StageVariables.Derivation:

THEN IF  Link_78.Acquisition__c = Link_78.DeptIn1Acquisition
      THEN Link_78.DateIn1

StageVariables.Derivation:
IF Link_82.InitialAcqDate < Link_82.DateOut1 AND (Link_82.Acquisition__c <> Link_82.DeptOut1Acquisition OR ISNULL(Link_82.DeptOut1Acquisition))
THEN Link_82.DateOut1
ELSE IF Link_82.InitialAcqDate < Link_82.DateOut2 AND (Link_82.Acquisition__c <> Link_82.DeptOut2Acquisition OR ISNULL(Link_82.DeptOut2Acquisition))
      THEN Link_82.DateOut2
      ELSE IF Link_82.InitialAcqDate < Link_82.DateOut3 AND (Link_82.Acquisition__c <> Link_82.DeptOut3Acquisition OR ISNULL(Link_82.DeptOut3Acquisition))
            THEN Link_82.DateOut3
            ELSE SetNull()
StageVariables.Name: transOut
